Why vendored
------------
ENFIELD's reproducibility commitment requires deterministic URSim image
builds. The custom URSim image (docker/ursim/Dockerfile) bakes this URCap
into the OSGi bundle directory so live URScript execution works without
PolyScope GUI interaction. Vendoring fixes the binary to a known SHA-256
across all reviewer build environments.

